Package: pearson.diagram
Type: Package
Title: Pearson Diagram
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Renswick Delvar
Maintainer: Renswick Delvar <renswick.delver@gmail.com>
Description: The Pearson Diagram R package provides tools to visualize distributions using Pearson Diagrams.
    This package provides a simple and effective way to visualize the skewness and kurtosis of known and custom distributions on the Pearson diagram.
